      "content": "it's not even a symptom. it's just the reality. people always say \"it gets better\" but that's just what they say to make themselves feel less awkward. what if it doesn't? what if this is just how it is now? the idea of pushing through another fifty years of this... honestly, even thinking about the future feels like a threat. it just feels easier to just stop. to just not have to worry about what comes next.",
